===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{context|linguistics|lang=en}} The use of a [[nonstandard]] form due to a belief that it is more [[formal]] or more [[correct]] than the corresponding standard form.
# {{context|linguistics|lang=en}} A nonstandard form so used.

====Usage notes====
* Since it is often a matter of some debate whether a given form is standard or correct, the use of the term ''hypercorrection'' is typically subjective.

